headline: TPA Technologies Named A Workday Staffing Partner
summary: TPA technologies, a leading technology consulting firm, today announced that it has signed a partnership agreement with Workday, Inc. (NASDAQ: WDAY), a leading provider of solutions to help organizations manage their people and money. This partnership will expand and enhance TPA technologies' ability to deliver Workday-certified talent to organizations implementing the Workday platform.
